title: Snow - Foundation T01 - T03 (sosich-Nemo-CST) cbr
description:
Eternal winter has frozen Europe for ever. In this hopeless world, eaten by orion's disease, the survival of the hunting horn clan lies in hunt and trade. Boris promised to take his people to the medics where his wife Edith could give birth to their child.
The shadow of death already hovers over this newborn child, because flesher made it his prey!
This tragedy will be played in blood and snow...

enjoy
